      "multimodalEnabled": true
    },
    "long_instructions": "\r\n## Do This:\r\n\r\n<br/>1. **Pick a scenario for your site map:**\r\n\r\n   * **Adopt-A-Pet** - a shelter web app for finding pets to adopt\r\n   * **School Shop** - a marketplace to buy, sell, or trade school supplies\r\n   * **City Explorer** - a web app to discover local events and places\r\n   * **Eco Challenge Tracker** - a web app to track habits and join eco challenges\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br/>2. **Outline a site map that at least includes:**\r\n\r\n   * A Homepage\r\n   * At least 3 main sections\r\n   * At least 2 levels of hierarchy\r\n\r\n   Write a quick list before using AI.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br/> 3. **Prompt AI Chat for feedback.**\r\n   Paste your outline, your selected scenario, and ask:\r\n\r\n   > Here's my site map for [insert selected scenario]. How can I make it clearer or better organized?\r\n",
    "display_name": "Co-Create with AI",
    "bubble_choice_description": "Work with AI to plan your site map. Outline your homepage, sections, and subpages, then refine your structure with feedback.",
